```python
class Solution:
    def distanceBetweenBusStops(self, distance: List[int], start: int, destination: int) -> int:
        if len(distance)==1:
            return distance[0]
        if start > destination:
        	start,destination = destination,start
        a = sum(distance[start:destination])
        del distance[start:destination]
        b = sum(distance)
        return min(a,b)
```        
